In [26]:



     


def symmetric_mean_absolute_percentage_error(target, prediction):
    numerator = np.abs(target - prediction)
    denominator = (np.abs(target) + np.abs(prediction)) / 2 
    smape = 1 / len(target) * np.sum(numerator / denominator) * 100
    return smape
